<br>
Now that anime is no longer an &quot;underground&quot; phenomena(using underground cuz I can't think of a better word.) like it was when I started watching it.  For younger people it's the same reason they have to get the 120 dollar shoes or whatever.  Because now its &quot;hip&quot; and &quot;in.&quot;  I don't have a problem with the fact that anime is more popular, that means more for us.  I don't like the people who get into something without really understanding what's BEHIND it.<br>
<br>
And then since it's popular you are going to have groups of people speaking out AGAINST it.  Which ticks off those of us who love Anime... but at the same time since the &quot;grown-up&quot; don't like it, more people have to get it.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/uanarchyao2.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AnarchyAo2</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Pre-Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(10/19/02 5:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1988.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   a</span><hr size=1> Yeah, alot of stupid people are out there.  SOME people think that i'm drawing pokemon but alot of people think that its cool.  Thou some complain about how the boobs are always too big, but i'm always like &quot;and your complaining about that....???&quot;  then they leave. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/ulordarquais.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lord Arquais</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(10/20/02 3:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1988.topic&index=23>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.liquid2k.net/jaheria/d.n.angel.gif width=84 height=120></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: a</span><hr size=1> and i thinks that it's because some people are jealous because they don't have any of their own anime to show around. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=flare60>flare60</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karb